The Josh Reaches A New High: Team Uri Celebrates The Success As It Heads Closer To 200 Cr Mark
The Josh Reaches A New High: Team Uri Celebrates The Success As It Heads Closer To 200 Cr Mark
To celebrate the success of Uri, the team hosted a bash last night in Mumbai. Just to jog your memory a little, the film managed to cross 8 crore on the first Wednesday of its release.
The success of the film was celebrated by the whole team.
Viral Bhayani
Not many know that the film has also broken Baahubali’s record on Day 23 and Day 24. While Baahubali collected Rs 6.35 crore on day 23 and Rs 7.8 crore on day 24, Uri managed to earn Rs 6.53 crore on day 23 and Rs 8.71 crore on day 24.
Present at the bash were Vicky Kaushal, Yami Gautam, Mohit Raina, Kirti Kulhari – director Aditya Dhar and producer Ronnie Screwvala. Have a look at the pictures.
